OL,3,CFormer teaching union head jailed
OL,4,Cafter conviction for sexually
OL,5,Cassaulting pupil
OL,7,FThe former head of a Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fteaching union David Baxter has been
OL,9,Fjailed for four-and-a-half months
OL,10,Fafter being convicted of sexually
OL,11,Fassaulting a pupil in his storeroom at
OL,12,FErne Integrated College in 2018.
OL,14,FThe Judge told the 65-year-old of
OL,15,FKilladeas Road in Lisnarick that
OL,16,FBaxter had shown a "complete denial of
OL,17,Fculpability" and "no remorse."
