OL,7,F"This matter is aggravated by the fact
OL,8,Fthat you abused your position of trust
OL,9,Fas a teacher. The victim was a
OL,10,Fvulnerable child whom you groomed, and
OL,11,Fyou were the architect of an
OL,12,Fopportunity to bring her into the
OL,13,Fstoreroom, where you sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted her.
OL,16,F"There is a high degree of harm in
OL,17,Fthis case, as the victim had to leave
OL,18,Fher school, and this has affected her
OL,19,Ffor the rest of her life.
