OL,7,F"In some distorted sense of reality,
OL,8,Fyou consider yourself a victim, and I
OL,9,Fregard that as an aggravating feature."
OL,11,FThe victim was in court for sentencing
OL,12,Fsupported by her family.
OL,14,FThe court heard Baxter maintains his
OL,15,Finnocence.
OL,17,FHe was granted bail and is set to
OL,18,Fappeal his conviction.
