OL,7,FIn a statement Erne Integrated College
OL,8,Fsaid: "The current board of governors
OL,9,Fof Erne Integrated College wishes
OL,10,Ffirst of all to repeat our abhorrence
OL,11,Fof the assault suffered by our former
OL,12,Fstudent.
OL,14,F"Our first thoughts are with the young
OL,15,Fwoman herself and her family.
OL,17,F"It is a source of pain and deep
OL,18,Fregret that she was subjected to abuse
OL,19,Fwithin our school, at a time when she
OL,20,Fshould have felt particularly safe and
OL,21,Fsecure.
